Title: Jung Duk
Description:
THIS. IS. WAR.

I will have the heads of everyone who took Lin from me. EVERYONE!

We will begin with the Osul leader, Jung Duk.

Take this Shado-Pan war banner and place it at the center of their camp.

Jung Duk will have no choice but to face you.

Show him no mercy, $n.
ObjectivesText: Plant the Shado-Pan Banner on the Ceremonial Pile, then kill Jung Duk.
PortraitGiverText: The leader of the Osul yaungol. Bring him down!
CompletionText: Jung Duk's legacy is written in the blood of innocents.
RewardText:
Jung Duk is dead at last.

Hundreds, perhaps thousands, lost their lives due to his violent aggression.

Though they are not here to witness his demise, they owe deep gratitude to your bravery today.
